cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.CL, cs.CR, cs.HC 

The paper is about the future of information retrieval (IR) and the development of non-mainstream ideas and research agendas in IR. This topic falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the workshop involved working on proposals of common interest, which could fall under the categories of Deep Learning (cs.DL) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The workshop also involved researchers from academia and industry, which could fall under the categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
